{panel:title=Atlassian Update - 21-08-2019|borderStyle=solid|borderColor=#3c78b5|titleBGColor=#3c78b5|bgColor=#e7f4fa}
After some analysis we've found that this ticket has been duplicated by the request at CONFCLOUD-36137 - Allow customized CSS in Confluence OnDemand.

Please cast your vote and watch that issue for further updates.
{panel}
We would like to have the same ability in confluence cloud as confluence server does for doing the custom CSS as in the article below.

[https://confluence.atlassian.com/doc/styling-fonts-in-confluence-174751968.html]

{color:#14892c}*Шаги к воспроизведению:*{color}
1. Запустить приложение "Komus".


{color:#14892c}*Фактический результат:*{color}
После запуска приложения определяет место расположения как г. Ростов-на-Дону

*{color:#14892c}Ожидаемый результат:{color}*
Место расположения г. Днепропетровск
